flowchart TD
    A["Identify principles applicable to this system"] --> B["Score each principle on 1-5 graded scale"]
    B --> C{"Score below threshold?"}

    C -->|"No"| D["Record adherence with evidence; close cycle"]
    C -->|"Yes"| E["Identify deviation evidence"]

    E --> F{"Categorise deviation"}

    F --> G["Deliberate trade-off (ADR exists)"]
    F --> H["Oversight (principle not considered)"]
    F --> I["Drift (originally adherent, has eroded)"]

    G --> J["Schedule trade-off revisitation; verify justification still holds"]
    H --> K["Generate debt item with near-term deadline"]
    I --> L["Trigger architectural review at practice level"]

    J --> M["Update scorecard with categorised deviation; close cycle"]
    K --> M
    L --> M

    M --> N["Aggregate debt across systems; review at practice level"]
    N --> O["Inform platform investment and capability development"]
